Name: P40-49
checklistText:
40 - SPS Thrusting
        Sequence of Events:
            V37E 40E
            Flashing V50 N18
                Desired IMU Attitude for burn
                    Roll(OG)    XXX.xx deg
                    Pitch(IG)   XXX.xx deg
                    Yaw(MG)     XXX.xx deg
            Pro to begin auto maneuver
            Solid V06 N18
                Same as above, auto maneuver in progress
            Flashing V50 N18
                Same as above, Maneuver complete.
            GDC align
            SPS Motors Energized
            S/C Control to SCS, SPS servo check and manual drive check performed
            S/C Control to CMC
            PRO
            Flashing V50 N18
                Same as N18 above, Vehicle is trimmed to burn altitude
            Enter
                Flashing V50N25
                    00204 - Perform Checklist item SPS gimbal trim
            Pro starts SPS gimbal test, Enter bypasses test
            SPS gimbals commanded to trim angles (P, Y)
            V60 N40
                TFI                         XXbxx Min/sec
                Velocity to be gained(Vg)   XXXX.x ft/s
                Accumulated Velocity(dV)    XXXX.x ft/s
            DSKY will blank at T-35, V60 N40 will auto resume at T-30
            Avg G - Auto ON
            Ullage initiated automatically if required using THC
            Flashing V99 N40
                Same as N40 above, press PRO to assent to burn.
            Auto Ignition at TFI = 0
            TVC DAP activated

            SPS Cut-off, burn complete
            
            TVC DAP Auto off
            Flashing V16 N40
                same as N40 above
            PRO
            Flashing V16 N85
                Vg Residuals    x XXXX.x ft/s
                                y XXXX.x ft/s
                                z XXXX.x ft/s
            Trim Residuals with THC if required
            PRO, If MINKEY is active, P76 is entered
            Flashing V37
                Manual Sequence
            V82E Request orbital parameter display
            Flashing V16 N44
                Apocenter Altitude (Ha)     XXXX.x nmi
                Pericenter Altitude (Hp)    XXXX.x nmi
                TFF                         XXbxx min/s
            PRO
            Flashing V37 - Select new program
            Average G Auto off

49 - Crew Defined Maneuver
    V06 N22 (Flashing):
        Desired attitude:   
            Roll:   XXX.xx deg
            Pitch:  XXX.xx deg
            Yaw:    XXX.xx deg
        Pro
    V50 N18 (Flashing):
        Confirm Active Maneuver Target: 
            Roll:   XXX.xx deg
            Pitch:  XXX.xx deg
            Yaw:    XXX.xx deg
    Ensure Pnl 2: RCS CMD - On
    Ensure Pnl 2: RCS Prplnt(/Helium) TB - Grey
    Ensure Pnl 8: AUTO RCS Select Switches (16) - MNA OR MNB
    Ensure Pnl 8: RCS Logic CB (2) - In
    Ensure Pnl 1: Rot Contr PWR Normal(2) - Ctr
    Ensure Pnl 1: Rot Contr PWR Direct(2) - Up
    Ensure Pnl 1: CMC Mode - Auto
    Pro
    V06 N18 (Flashing): Auto Maneuver Proceeding
        Active Maneuver Target:
            Roll:   XXX.xx deg
            Pitch:  XXX.xx deg
            Yaw:    XXX.xx deg
    Pro
    Routine end, Automaneuver continues
    End Automaneuver with CMC Mode - Free
